{"tid":541833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賤種范國威未獲確認參選資格   斥行政干預選舉","createTime":"2018-01-27T01:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T06:13:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f782c8979ee9427ba75febce609dc17b5bca3616","tid":541833,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180126/large/1516978631_b307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180126%2Flarge%2F1516978631_b307.jpg&h=10716e72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n代表民主派參選立法會補選3名參選人，除了姚松炎、周庭未獲確認參選資格，盛傳會遭當局DQ外，代表民主派出戰新東議席的新同盟范國威，同樣至昨日都未獲確認參選資格，范國威批評當局拖延處理審批，透過行政手段干預選舉。<br />\n<br />\n4名代表民主派參加3.11初選的人士中，暫時只有參選建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界公專聯司馬文獲確認參選資格。前年成功入閘參選立會的范國威回覆《蘋果》查詢時強調，無論他或姚、周都不應被當局DQ，而當局若要DQ他更是絕不合理，除非港府強行將提倡本土都與港獨扣連，惟這無疑是官媒的手法。<br />\n<br />\n范又指，他昨日只收到當局回覆其競選團隊指，目前仍在跟進有關確認其參選資格的事宜，所以未能回應有關進度及原因。他指出，一般而言選舉事務處只需4、5天時間就能確認參選資格，前年他參與立法會大選，都在較短時間內獲確認參選資格，但今次他報名滿一星期仍未獲批，強調當局再不確認他與姚、周的參選資格，就是透過行政手段干預選舉，使民主派難就選舉作部署。<br />\n<br />\n另外，佔旺刑事藐視法庭案被告之一、前學聯常委司徒子朗昨於社交網發文，批評下周一報名參選的民主黨袁海文支持度低，不能代表初選多數選民立場，希望資助有志之士參選立法會九龍西補選。"},{"pid":"043d842f8f0c4f5acb61e4d85d261ea016649937","tid":541833,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:06:18.000Z","msg":"官逼民反 但港奴不會反"},{"pid":"51ead908f1f990ba7c6a2d494e4afa30b54c3b4a","tid":541833,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:11:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ef8f634ecf711ff08f6994052af35b173f598ff","tid":541833,"uid":5499,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:54:01.000Z","msg":"今次我撐范國威<br />\n<br />\n明明咁忠心，咁都未確認，有無搞錯"},{"pid":"aea206d2db75136b8f72f8069e9a80ed4c4e564b","tid":541833,"uid":130262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ef8f634ecf711ff08f6994052af35b173f598ff","tid":541833,"uid":5499,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:54:01.000Z","msg":"今次我撐范國威<br />\n<br />\n明明咁忠心，咁都未確認，有無搞錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f3a604e985f8ecd267de8d1f85651cb0c359b6","tid":541833,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:37:56.000Z","msg":"而家係等中央確認"},{"pid":"5e22dde377fce44c32d7123d39a00b55c7bb5b2d","tid":541833,"uid":142888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"全部錯重點，而家重點唔係泛民點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重點係政府玩嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6f99f11fd86dd3f6fec355a623db43f5a7fc60","tid":541833,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1add06f80a6179fe2ef6a39eec7c0c675f27844f","tid":541833,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:58:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"479c463b1b1a7614ff664ca905576db8e07f3eea","tid":541833,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"自認中國人都唔順利入閘？！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4d02d6f7b223a18e3fb3ffe8c95a0a84c0da2d","tid":541833,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:13:28.000Z","msg":"佢絕對係傳統泛民喎 咁都唔放？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}